14:43.416 --> 14:47.654
- MAYBE HE THOUGHT I WAS
BEST QUALIFIED FOR THE JOB.

14:47.687 --> 14:50.123
- OR MAYBE HE'S JUST TRYING
TO WIN YOU BACK.

14:50.157 --> 14:53.193
- HE CAN TRY
ALL HE WANTS.

14:53.226 --> 14:55.128
