16:32.459 --> 16:35.762
- WELL, WHEN DO YOU WANT IT?

16:35.795 --> 16:37.364
- I DON'T.

16:37.397 --> 16:39.299
- THERE'S BEEN A SLIGHT CHANGE
OF PLANS.

16:39.332 --> 16:43.770
