17:07.694 --> 17:08.728
- BUT IF WE GET SOMEONE ELSE,

17:08.761 --> 17:09.796
OUR KIDS WON'T BE RELATED.

17:09.829 --> 17:11.398
- HAVE YOU EVER MET MY SISTER?

17:11.431 --> 17:13.166
THAT'S NOT MUCH OF AN ARGUMENT.
- WE HAD A DEAL.

17:13.200 --> 17:17.570
- YOU'RE THE ONES
THAT CHANGED THE TERMS.

17:17.604 --> 17:19.472
ME AND MELANIE,
MOM AND POP.

17:19.506 --> 17:21.341
