17:21.374 --> 17:23.210
- * LEND A HAND

17:23.243 --> 17:26.179
- I'D SAY THAT WENT WELL.

17:27.480 --> 17:29.282
- JESUS CHRIST!

17:29.316 --> 17:30.850
