EAT HERE?

17:30.883 --> 17:32.685
- THEY'RE ALL FRESH AND NEW.

17:32.719 --> 17:34.687
- HAND-PICKED
FROM THE PLEASURE BOUTIQUE.

17:34.721 --> 17:36.156
[sniffs]
MMM.

17:36.189 --> 17:37.824
- I JUST WANT TO SLEEP
WITH THE GUY,

17:37.857 --> 17:39.459
NOT DRILL FOR OIL.

17:39.492 --> 17:40.560
- WELL, THAT'S WHY
WE BROUGHT THESE,

17:40.593 --> 17:42.195
TO HELP YOU ACHIEVE YOUR GOAL.

17:42.229 --> 17:46.299
WHICH WOULD YOU SAY MOST
RESEMBLES DETECTIVE HORVATH?

17:46.333 --> 17:47.834
- HOW THE HELL
WOULD I KNOW?

17:47.867 --> 17:49.602
I'VE ONLY KISSED HIM.

17:49.636 --> 17:51.704
NOW PUT THOSE THINGS AWAY.

17:51.738 --> 17:53.473
- NOT SO FAST.

17:53.506 --> 17:55.242
NOW, YOU ASKED
FOR OUR HELP,

17:55.275 --> 17:57.444
AND THAT'S WHY WE'VE COME
TO TEACH YOU.

17:57.477 --> 17:59.846
- THE ART OF ORAL SEX.

17:59.879 --> 18:01.481
- WE'RE GOING TO SHARE
WITH YOU SECRETS

18:01.514 --> 18:04.217
KNOWN HERETOFORE
ONLY TO GAY MEN.

18:04.251 --> 18:06.853
- TECHNIQUES PASSED DOWN
FROM GENERATION TO GENERATION

18:06.886 --> 18:08.321
SINCE TIME IMMEMORIAL.

18:08.355 --> 18:09.722
- ONCE YOU'VE PASSED
THE COURSE,

18:09.756 --> 18:12.325
WE GUARANTEE HORVATH
WILL FOREVER REGARD YOU

18:12.359 --> 18:14.761
AS HIS GODDESS,
HIS QUEEN.

18:14.794 --> 18:17.197
- CLEOPATRA, SCHEHERAZADE,

18:17.230 --> 18:18.631
REESE WITHERSPOON.

18:18.665 --> 18:20.233
- [sighs]

18:20.267 --> 18:21.868
