18:26.306 --> 18:28.808
ROTATING IT FIRST CLOCKWISE...

18:28.841 --> 18:29.876
UH-HUH.

18:29.909 --> 18:31.344
THEN COUNTERCLOCKWISE...

18:31.378 --> 18:33.513
UH-HUH.
YEAH. GOOD.

18:33.546 --> 18:34.514
NOW WAG THE TONGUE.

18:34.547 --> 18:35.615
AH, AH, AH.

18:35.648 --> 18:36.616
AH, AH, AH, AH,
AH, AH, AH, AH.

18:36.649 --> 18:37.650
YEAH, THAT'S THE WAY.

18:37.684 --> 18:40.220
- NEXT, GRASP THE SHAFT FIRMLY

18:40.253 --> 18:41.288
WITH OUR RIGHT HAND,

18:41.321 --> 18:43.223
LEFT IF WE'RE A SOUTHPAW--

18:43.256 --> 18:44.891
CREATING A VELVET VISE.

18:44.924 --> 18:47.260
- MMM.

18:47.294 --> 18:48.628
NOW OPEN WIDE...

18:48.661 --> 18:50.763
[muffled]
BEING SURE TO COVER THE TEETH,

18:50.797 --> 18:53.800
ALLOWING FOR A SMOOTH
AND UNOBSTRUCTED ENTRY.

18:53.833 --> 18:56.703
COMME CA.
[inhales]

18:59.439 --> 19:02.242
- BOYS,
YOU KNOW I LOVE YOU.

19:02.275 --> 19:04.244
I JUST NEED
TO ASK ONE QUESTION.

19:04.277 --> 19:05.712
- IF IT'S ABOUT SUPPRESSING
THE GAG REFLEX,

19:05.745 --> 19:07.180
WE'RE GETTING TO THAT.

19:07.214 --> 19:10.650
- ARE YOU
OUT OF YOUR FUCKING MINDS?

19:10.683 --> 19:12.952
THERE'S NO WAY
I'M GONNA DO THIS.

19:12.985 --> 19:15.188
- THERE ARE PARTIES
IN BEVERLY HILLS

19:15.222 --> 19:17.390
WHERE HOUSEWIVES PAY
1,000 BUCKS A HEAD.

19:17.424 --> 19:18.791
- SO TO SPEAK.

19:18.825 --> 19:20.927
- TO LEARN WHAT
WE'RE TEACHING YOU FOR FREE.

19:20.960 --> 19:22.562
- DEBBIE,

19:22.595 --> 19:25.532
YOU WANT TO MAKE HORVATH HAPPY,
DON'T YOU?

19:25.565 --> 19:27.267
- SURE, I DO.

19:27.300 --> 19:29.469
- AND EVEN HAVE
A GOOD TIME YOURSELF?

19:29.502 --> 19:31.338
- SO WHAT'S THE HARM
IN LEARNING

19:31.371 --> 19:35.174
HOW TO DO IT
THE RIGHT WAY?

19:40.847 --> 19:44.217
[inhales deeply]

19:51.391 --> 19:54.461
men: ONE...

19:54.494 --> 19:55.828
TWO...

19:55.862 --> 19:56.963
[all inhaling]

19:56.996 --> 20:01.901
[indistinct chatter]

20:23.790 --> 20:25.024
- IT'S CHILLY OUT HERE.

20:25.057 --> 20:28.227
