TO GET S--

20:29.362 --> 20:31.998
- THANK YOU.

20:32.031 --> 20:34.267
I AM ALL RIGHT.

20:35.768 --> 20:39.005
- I'M SORRY.

20:39.038 --> 20:41.408
- FOR WHAT?

20:41.441 --> 20:43.410
- FOR PAUL.
FOR YOU.

20:43.443 --> 20:47.647
- I JUST DIDN'T EXPECT IT
TO BE SO SOON.

20:47.680 --> 20:51.751
IF I'D KNOWN, I WOULD'VE GONE
TO SEE HIM MORE OFTEN.

20:51.784 --> 20:53.620
- YOU WERE BUSY.

20:53.653 --> 20:56.823
- YEAH, RIGHT.

20:56.856 --> 20:58.491
THAT'S ALWAYS A GOOD EXCUSE,
NOT TO VISIT SOMEONE

20:58.525 --> 21:00.927
YOU ONCE SHARED YOUR LIFE WITH,
YOUR BED.

21:00.960 --> 21:04.897
- I'M SURE HE UNDERSTOOD.

21:04.931 --> 21:07.567
AND FORGAVE YOU THE SAME WAY
YOU FORGAVE HIM.

21:07.600 --> 21:11.638
- THEN WHY AM I SO GODDAMN ANGRY
AT HIM RIGHT NOW?

21:11.671 --> 21:15.542
FOR GETTING IT,
FOR GIVING IT TO ME.

21:15.575 --> 21:16.976
AND THEN NOT EVEN BOTHERING

21:17.009 --> 21:18.978
TO TAKE CARE OF HIMSELF
OR WATCH WHAT HE ATE.

21:19.011 --> 21:21.381
