"NUTRITION IS ESSENTIAL.

21:21.414 --> 21:22.515
"AND EXERCISE.

21:22.549 --> 21:23.516
"YOU'VE GOT TO EXERCISE, PAUL,

21:23.550 --> 21:24.817
BUILD UP YOUR MUSCLE MASS."

21:24.851 --> 21:28.555
