"I'M GOING TO DIE ANYWAY,

21:32.492 --> 21:36.028
SO WHAT THE HELL DIFFERENCE
DOES IT MAKE?"

21:37.697 --> 21:41.100
- LUCKILY,
YOU'RE NOT LIKE THAT.

21:41.133 --> 21:42.802
- RIGHT.

21:42.835 --> 21:45.004
- YOU DO EVERYTHING
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO DO.

21:45.037 --> 21:47.407
EVERYTHING YOU CAN POSSIBLY DO.
- AND IN SPITE OF EVERYTHING,

21:47.440 --> 21:48.475
I STILL ENDED UP
IN THE HOSPITAL.

21:48.508 --> 21:51.344
MAYBE HE'S RIGHT.

21:51.378 --> 21:52.412
MAYBE IT DOESN'T MATTER.

21:52.445 --> 21:53.946
- IT DOES MATTER.

21:53.980 --> 21:57.884
AND MOST IMPORTANT IS
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE IT DOES.

22:16.168 --> 22:17.637
- MORE COD?

22:17.670 --> 22:18.771
- OH.

22:18.805 --> 22:20.973
3 GRAMS,
I'M STUFFED.

22:21.007 --> 22:22.509
[laughter]

22:22.542 --> 22:23.910
- WELL, THERE'S FRUIT
FOR DESSERT.

22:23.943 --> 22:26.045
