EXCITING, BUT--

22:26.078 --> 22:28.615
- WITH YOU IN THE ROOM,
WHAT COULD BE?

22:31.083 --> 22:33.920
- I'LL GET THE FRUIT.

22:35.488 --> 22:36.923
- FORGET THE FRUIT.

22:36.956 --> 22:37.990
- OH.

22:38.024 --> 22:39.158
- I'VE GOT A BETTER IDEA.

22:39.191 --> 22:40.159
- I'M TOO HEAVY,
YOU--

22:40.192 --> 22:43.362
- YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

22:44.664 --> 22:47.033
- CARL...

22:47.066 --> 22:49.135
