THAT IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME.

23:02.982 --> 23:06.686
- HOW LONG?

23:06.719 --> 23:08.888
- LAST CENTURY.

23:08.921 --> 23:12.425
- WELL, DON'T WORRY
ABOUT IT.

23:12.459 --> 23:14.794
I PROMISE TO BE GENTLE,
GUIDE YOU THROUGH IT.

23:14.827 --> 23:18.064
MAYBE EVEN TEACH YOU
A FEW THINGS.

23:25.071 --> 23:29.642
- THE EXPRESSION ON HIS FACE
NEEDS TO BE MORE ENTICING,

23:29.676 --> 23:32.979
BUT MORE FOREBODING.

23:33.012 --> 23:36.716
"ENTER AT YOUR OWN RISK.
PREPARE TO BE FUCKED."

23:36.749 --> 23:39.852
- THINK I CAN MANAGE THAT.

23:39.886 --> 23:41.521
- YOU COULD PROBABLY GET
A BETTER VIEW

23:41.554 --> 23:44.491
IF YOU STOOD
A LITTLE CLOSER.

23:47.994 --> 23:49.962
AND HIS HIPS NEED
TO BE MORE IN PROFILE

23:49.996 --> 23:52.865
TO ACCENTUATE HIS COCK.

23:52.899 --> 23:54.601
- IT'S ALWAYS ABOUT SEX.

23:54.634 --> 23:56.836
- UNLESS IT'S ABOUT DEATH,
BUT...

23:56.869 --> 23:58.805
DEATH DOESN'T SELL TICKETS.

23:58.838 --> 24:00.540
[door sliding]

24:00.573 --> 24:02.509
- I PICKED UP
CHINESE FOOD.

24:05.712 --> 24:07.947
I DIDN'T KNOW
IT WAS FOR THREE.

24:07.980 --> 24:11.217
- I WAS JUST GOING.

24:11.250 --> 24:14.186
WE'RE DONE, RIGHT?

24:17.524 --> 24:19.158
- HEY.
- HEY.

24:19.191 --> 24:22.161
- SO GLAD YOU BOYS KISSED
AND MADE UP.

24:22.194 --> 24:24.030
