24:24.063 --> 24:25.131
HOW MUCH DO I OWE YOU?

24:25.164 --> 24:26.566
- IT'S ON ME.

24:26.599 --> 24:31.003
- HMM.
WELL, IN THAT CASE,

24:31.037 --> 24:35.608
