- HIS, UH...
[clears throat]

25:54.854 --> 25:58.057
HIS EX, PAUL,
THE ONE WHO INFECTED HIM...

25:58.090 --> 26:00.793
- * YOU'LL GO IT ALONE,
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID *

26:00.827 --> 26:01.861
- DIED.
- * EVER SINCE YOU'VE BECOME

26:01.894 --> 26:03.596
* THE WALKING DEAD

26:03.630 --> 26:06.332
- WHAT A WONDERFUL WORLD.

26:06.365 --> 26:09.068
YOU HAVE TO BE NUTS

26:09.101 --> 26:11.203
OR A SELFISH PIECE OF SHIT

26:11.237 --> 26:13.606
TO WANT TO BRING
A CHILD INTO IT.

26:13.640 --> 26:15.875
- [snorts] YOU DID.

26:15.908 --> 26:18.244
- YEAH, LINDSAY CONVINCED ME
ONE NIGHT WHEN I WAS TRIPPING.

26:18.277 --> 26:22.815
[laughter]

26:22.849 --> 26:24.383
BUT I'M SURE AS HELL
NOT DOING IT

26:24.416 --> 26:26.085
FOR SMELLY MELLY.

26:26.118 --> 26:27.253
THEY CAN GO
TO A SPERM BANK.

26:27.286 --> 26:29.088
- OR SCRAPE IT
OFF THE FLOOR

26:29.121 --> 26:30.823
IN THE BACK ROOM
AT BABYLON.

26:30.857 --> 26:33.726
- [sniffs]
- [laughs]

26:33.760 --> 26:35.828
- JUST GIVE ME
ONE VALID REASON

26:35.862 --> 26:37.296
WHY ANY QUEER
IN HIS RIGHT MIND

26:37.329 --> 26:39.866
WOULD WANT TO BRING A KID
INTO THIS WORLD.

26:39.899 --> 26:42.134
- UM...
[sirens wail]

26:42.168 --> 26:44.103
- CAN'T THINK OF ONE,
CAN YOU?

26:44.136 --> 26:46.739
- WAIT A MINUTE.
WAIT, HOLD ON.

26:46.773 --> 26:49.008
- * I'D LIKE TO THINK
YOU MAYBE UNDERSTAND *

26:49.041 --> 26:54.246
* WHY I EVEN BOTHER
TO OFFER MY HAND *

26:54.280 --> 26:56.315
- TO PISS OFF
STRAIGHT PEOPLE.

26:56.348 --> 27:02.321
[laughter]

27:02.354 --> 27:04.857
- [sighs]

27:04.891 --> 27:06.759
- YOU'RE NOT DISAPPOINTED,
ARE YOU?

27:06.793 --> 27:08.294
- DISAPPOINTED?

27:08.327 --> 27:11.030
OH.

27:11.063 --> 27:12.732
MORE LIKE AMAZED.

27:12.765 --> 27:15.167
- REALLY?

27:15.201 --> 27:17.003
- ESPECIALLY AFTER

27:17.036 --> 27:20.673
ALL THAT LIP SERVICE
ABOUT HOW NERVOUS YOU WERE.

27:22.474 --> 27:24.010
- WHAT'S THAT MEAN?

27:24.043 --> 27:26.212
- AH.

27:26.245 --> 27:28.014
NOTHING.

27:28.047 --> 27:31.283
- DON'T GIVE ME "NOTHING"
AFTER A REMARK LIKE THAT.

27:31.317 --> 27:34.153
- LET'S JUST SAY THAT

27:34.186 --> 27:36.823
NO ONE COULD DO WHAT YOU JUST
DID WITHOUT A LITTLE PRACTICE.

27:36.856 --> 27:41.327
AND FROM THE WAY THAT YOU,
UH, YOU KNOW...

27:41.360 --> 27:45.064
LADY,
YOU COULD TEACH A CLASS.

27:45.097 --> 27:46.833
- IS THAT SO?

27:46.866 --> 27:49.035
- IN FACT, I HEARD
IN BEVERLY HILLS

27:49.068 --> 27:51.103
THEY CHARGE $1,000 FOR IT.

27:51.137 --> 27:53.773
- HORVATH, I WAS TELLING YOU
THE TRUTH.

27:53.806 --> 27:55.775
THIS IS THE FIRST TIME
IN YEARS THAT I...

27:55.808 --> 27:58.444
- YEAH, SURE.
WHATEVER.

27:58.477 --> 28:01.413
- YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME?

28:05.217 --> 28:06.953
WELL, THAT'S JUST
TOO FUCKING BAD.

28:06.986 --> 28:08.921
NOW YOU BETTER TAKE
YOUR SUSPICIONS

28:08.955 --> 28:10.823
AND YOUR SUSPENDERS,

28:10.857 --> 28:13.059
AND--AND REMOVE YOUR BUTT
FROM MY BED!

28:13.092 --> 28:16.929
- DEBBIE...
- NOW, OUT!

28:16.963 --> 28:19.131
GET OUT!

28:28.107 --> 28:30.943
- HERE'S YOUR FEE.

28:30.977 --> 28:32.511
PLUS $100 BONUS
FOR FINISHING ON TIME.

28:32.544 --> 28:34.981
- THANKS.

28:35.014 --> 28:36.883
- AND HERE'S TWO TICKETS
FOR TONIGHT.

28:36.916 --> 28:39.351
ONE FOR YOU
AND ONE FOR IAN.

28:39.385 --> 28:44.156
- OH, UM...

28:44.190 --> 28:45.491
- I WAS JUST ADMIRING

28:45.524 --> 28:47.093
YOUR BOYFRIEND'S
LATEST CREATION.

28:47.126 --> 28:48.761
- AN ARTIST ALWAYS DOES
HIS BEST WORK

28:48.795 --> 28:50.763
WHEN HE HAS SOMEBODY
HE LOVES TO INSPIRE HIM.

28:50.797 --> 28:53.232
- [chuckles]
YEAH, SO I'VE BEEN TOLD.

28:53.265 --> 28:55.902
- WE SHOULD GO.
- SEE YOU TONIGHT.

28:55.935 --> 28:58.270
- OH, BRIAN GAVE US TICKETS
TO THE CENTER CARNIVAL.

28:58.304 --> 29:00.439
- OH, I'M SURE
IT'LL BE A BLAST,

29:00.472 --> 29:02.074
BUT WE'VE ALREADY GOT PLANS.

29:02.108 --> 29:04.276
- OH, WELL,
IF YOU CHANGE YOUR MINDS,

29:04.310 --> 29:07.513
YOUR NAMES WILL BE
ON THE LIST.

29:07.546 --> 29:09.115
- SO HOW YOU DOING?

29:09.148 --> 29:11.117
- OH, UM...
WHY AREN'T YOU IN CLASS?

29:11.150 --> 29:14.053
I THOUGHT
YOU HAD A CLASS.

29:18.424 --> 29:20.793
- ORDER'S UP
ON TABLE FOUR.

29:20.827 --> 29:22.862
[indistinct chatter]

29:22.895 --> 29:24.997
- THE SPECIAL TODAY
IS THE DICK OF DEATH.

29:25.031 --> 29:27.299
FOOT-LONG HOT DOG,
CREAMY COLESLAW ON THE SIDE.

29:27.333 --> 29:29.535
DON'T MAKE ME REPEAT IT.

29:29.568 --> 29:32.404
both: TWO SPECIALS.

29:32.438 --> 29:33.940
- WAIT, WAIT, WAIT!

29:33.973 --> 29:35.307
SO HOW WAS IT?

29:35.341 --> 29:36.809
- YEAH, SHOULD YOUR PROFESSORS
GIVE YOU AN "A"?

29:36.843 --> 29:39.011
- YEAH.
FOR "ASSHOLE."

29:39.045 --> 29:41.447
'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT I AM
FOR LISTENING TO YOU.

29:41.480 --> 29:44.350
- WHAT, HE WASN'T PLEASED?
- IMPOSSIBLE!

29:44.383 --> 29:46.018
I DEFY ANY MALE,
LIVING OR DEAD,

29:46.052 --> 29:47.553
NOT TO RESPOND
TO OUR TIME-TESTED TECHNIQUE.

29:47.586 --> 29:50.056
- PROVIDED YOU FOLLOWED
OUR INSTRUCTIONS.

29:50.089 --> 29:51.423
- OH, I FOLLOWED 'EM.

29:51.457 --> 29:53.893
HE RESPONDED
TO EVERY FLICK AND LICK.

29:53.926 --> 29:55.294
- AND SO
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

29:55.327 --> 29:57.296
- THE PROBLEM IS HE THINKS
I'M A WHORE.

29:57.329 --> 30:00.032
- I'M SO PROUD.

30:00.066 --> 30:03.502
- WELL, I NEVER WANT
TO SEE HIM AGAIN.

30:07.606 --> 30:09.608
[bell rings]
NEW ORDER.

30:09.641 --> 30:12.044
- CAN I GET A B.L.T.?
- YEAH.

30:12.078 --> 30:14.914
- OOH, WHAT ABOUT 873?

30:14.947 --> 30:16.983
6'2", BLUE EYES,

30:17.016 --> 30:19.051
AND A MENSA!

30:19.085 --> 30:20.352
- IS THAT
WHAT YOU REALLY WANT?

30:20.386 --> 30:22.588
TO GIVE BIRTH
TO A LITTLE 873 1/2?

30:22.621 --> 30:24.623
- GOT CREAM.

30:24.656 --> 30:26.458
- [groans]

30:26.492 --> 30:29.128
- IT WAS MILKED FRESH
THIS MORNING.

30:29.161 --> 30:31.630
I SHOULD KNOW.
I MILKED IT MYSELF.

30:31.663 --> 30:32.932
- [giggles]

30:32.965 --> 30:33.933
- [mockingly laughs]

30:33.966 --> 30:35.001
THAT'S DISGUSTING.

30:35.034 --> 30:36.468
- THAT'S REALLY DISGUSTING.

30:36.502 --> 30:37.503
- YO, BITCHES,

30:37.536 --> 30:40.339
I'M OFFERING TO LEND A HAND.

30:40.372 --> 30:42.008
- WOULD YOU BEAT IT?

30:42.041 --> 30:43.109
- THAT'S WHAT
I'VE BEEN OFFERING TO DO.

30:43.142 --> 30:44.944
- WAIT.
DO YOU REALLY MEAN IT?

30:44.977 --> 30:47.646
- YEAH. IF IT'S A BOY,
YOU CAN NAME HIM BRIAN JUNIOR.

30:47.679 --> 30:49.481
- AND IF IT'S A GIRL?

30:49.515 --> 30:53.252
- CHARITY.
IN HONOR OF MY DONATION.

30:53.285 --> 30:57.423
NOW LET'S GO PISS OFF
SOME HETEROSEXUALS.

30:57.456 --> 30:58.490
- HMM.

30:58.524 --> 31:01.227
[pop music]

31:01.260 --> 31:09.201
*

31:52.311 --> 31:55.547
- HEY. ROY.
HOW YOU DOING?

31:55.581 --> 31:57.016
LISTEN, I WAS--

31:57.049 --> 31:58.284
I WAS WONDERING,
COULD YOU

31:58.317 --> 31:59.685
GIVE ME SOME HELP, MAN?

31:59.718 --> 32:02.488
- YOU WANT ME
TO SPOT YOU?

32:02.521 --> 32:06.592
- ACTUALLY, IT'S GOT MORE
TO DO WITH NUTRITION.

32:06.625 --> 32:08.360
SUPPLEMENTS...

32:08.394 --> 32:10.329
IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

32:10.362 --> 32:13.332
- YEAH.
COME ON.

32:28.480 --> 32:31.650
[indistinct chatter]

32:31.683 --> 32:32.718
- THERE'S GOT TO BE
MORE TO IT.

32:32.751 --> 32:38.190
[indistinct conversation]

32:38.224 --> 32:39.625
- HE ARRESTED ME,
THAT'S WHY.

32:39.658 --> 32:43.195
HE LIKES YOU, THOUGH.
HE THINKS YOU'RE FUNNY.

32:43.229 --> 32:46.999
- EXCUSE US,
DETECTIVE HORVATH?

32:47.033 --> 32:48.000
- [clears throat]

32:48.034 --> 32:49.735
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU BOYS?

32:49.768 --> 32:52.471
- WELL, A DEAR FRIEND
OF OURS

32:52.504 --> 32:54.606
IS IN A LITTLE BIT
OF TROUBLE.

32:54.640 --> 32:57.376
- SEEMS LAST NIGHT,

32:57.409 --> 33:02.514
AN ORAL...MISDEMEANOR
OCCURRED.

33:04.250 --> 33:07.186
- DON'T YOU HAVE
SOME WORK TO DO?

33:09.121 --> 33:10.389
WHAT THE HELL'S
ALL THIS ABOUT?

33:10.422 --> 33:13.225
- LOOK, DEBBIE TOLD US
THAT YOU HAD SEX,

33:13.259 --> 33:16.395
OR SOME HETEROSEXUAL
PERMUTATION THEREOF.

33:16.428 --> 33:17.663
- JESUS H. CHRIST.

33:17.696 --> 33:19.265
WHY DOESN'T SHE RENT
A BILLBOARD?

33:19.298 --> 33:21.633
WHAT WE DO IN BED
IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

33:21.667 --> 33:22.634
- ACTUALLY, IT IS.

33:22.668 --> 33:25.371
SEE, UM, DEBBIE WAS WORRIED

33:25.404 --> 33:27.506
THAT SHE WOULDN'T LIVE UP
TO YOUR EXPECTATIONS.

33:27.539 --> 33:29.241
- THAT SHE'D LET YOU DOWN.

33:29.275 --> 33:31.577
SO WE GAVE HER
A CRASH COURSE.

33:31.610 --> 33:33.812
- "INTRODUCTION
TO FELLATIO 101."

33:33.845 --> 33:36.115
- EMMETT'S ONE OF THE WORLD'S
FOREMOST AUTHORITIES.

33:36.148 --> 33:38.384
- AW, THANKS.
UH, ANYWAY.

33:38.417 --> 33:40.652
YOUNG DEBORAH PASSED
WITH HONORS.

33:40.686 --> 33:42.254
- MAGNA CUM LOUDLY.

33:42.288 --> 33:44.290
- IN FACT, SHE DID SO WELL,

33:44.323 --> 33:45.391
YOU, APPARENTLY...

33:45.424 --> 33:46.392
- AND MISGUIDEDLY--

33:46.425 --> 33:47.693
- THINK SHE'S A SLUT.

33:47.726 --> 33:50.062
THE TRUTH IS, DETECTIVE,

33:50.096 --> 33:51.797
WE'RE THE SLUTS.

33:51.830 --> 33:54.800
- SPEAK FOR YOURSELF.

33:54.833 --> 33:56.402
[clears throat]
LOOK.

33:56.435 --> 33:59.405
UNDERNEATH ALL THAT DIRTY TALK
AND BRAVADO,

33:59.438 --> 34:02.274
YOU KNOW, DEBBIE IS JUST
AN OLD-FASHIONED GIRL

34:02.308 --> 34:04.343
WHOSE ONLY CRIME WAS

34:04.376 --> 34:07.346
WANTING TO PLEASE HER MAN.

34:11.650 --> 34:14.620
AH.

34:18.257 --> 34:20.592
OH, HONEY.

34:20.626 --> 34:22.428
- RUMOR HAS IT
A CERTAIN FINALIST

34:22.461 --> 34:24.330
IS OUT OF THE COMPETITION.

34:24.363 --> 34:26.165
- OH, POOR MARTA.

34:26.198 --> 34:28.500
SHE'S AN ASTONISHING TALENT,
BUT TERRIFIED TO PERFORM.

34:28.534 --> 34:30.169
- AND THIS WILL BE THE TREE
IN THE FOREST

34:30.202 --> 34:31.303
THAT NOBODY HEARS.

34:31.337 --> 34:32.571
- AND THEN THERE'S GIORGIO.

34:32.604 --> 34:33.705
MEDIOCRE MUSICIAN AT BEST.

34:33.739 --> 34:35.174
- YEAH, BUT YOU PUT HIM
IN FRONT

34:35.207 --> 34:36.475
OF AN AUDIENCE,
HE KNOCKS 'EM DEAD.

34:36.508 --> 34:37.743
- NEW YORK
ISN'T PITTSBURGH.

34:37.776 --> 34:39.311
THEY WON'T BE
SO EASILY FOOLED.

34:39.345 --> 34:41.647
- YOU, MY DEAR, HAVE NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

34:41.680 --> 34:43.382
- [chuckles]

34:43.415 --> 34:44.450
[indistinct chatter]

34:44.483 --> 34:46.852
ABSOLUTELY, ABSOLUTELY.

34:46.885 --> 34:48.354
NO QUESTION ABOUT IT.

34:48.387 --> 34:51.323
- * I CANNOT HEAR

34:51.357 --> 34:54.193
- EXCUSE ME.

34:54.226 --> 34:57.629
HOLD ON.

34:57.663 --> 34:59.765
- * THIS IS NOT REAL

34:59.798 --> 35:01.233
- HAVING FUN?

35:01.267 --> 35:03.869
- YEAH, IT'S GREAT.

35:03.902 --> 35:05.504
- LIAR.

35:05.537 --> 35:08.740
- NO, YOUR FRIENDS ARE
REALLY SMART AND FUNNY.

35:08.774 --> 35:12.211
I GUESS I'M JUST NERVOUS,
THAT'S ALL.

35:12.244 --> 35:13.645
- AH, DON'T BE.

35:13.679 --> 35:15.681
YOU'RE WITH ME.

35:15.714 --> 35:19.418
- * WHATEVER YOU FIND

35:19.451 --> 35:22.521
- SO THIS IS
THE IMAGINARY BOYFRIEND.

35:22.554 --> 35:24.390
ETHAN TELLS ME
YOU'RE AN ARTIST.

35:24.423 --> 35:26.225
- YEP.
THAT'S RIGHT.

35:26.258 --> 35:27.626
- WHAT KIND OF STUFF
DO YOU DO?

35:27.659 --> 35:29.828
- LATELY, I'VE BEEN MANIPULATING
CLASSICAL FORM

35:29.861 --> 35:31.563
WITH DIGITAL IMAGERY.

35:31.597 --> 35:34.766
- HMM. THEN YOU'RE NOT
JUST A PRETTY FACE.

35:34.800 --> 35:36.635
- NO.

35:36.668 --> 35:38.804
I GOT A PRETTY BIG COCK
AS WELL,

35:38.837 --> 35:40.506
AND I GIVE
ONE HELL OF A BLOW JOB.

35:40.539 --> 35:41.640
RIGHT, ETHAN?

35:41.673 --> 35:44.410
- UM...

35:44.443 --> 35:47.379
- TIME TO RING
AROUND THE DILDO!

35:47.413 --> 35:48.647
- OH, MY GOD!

35:48.680 --> 35:52.251
- WELCOME TO CARNIVAL!

35:52.284 --> 35:54.186
- [laughs]

35:54.220 --> 35:58.257
[dance music]

35:58.290 --> 35:59.925
- IT'S TIME
FOR BUTTHOLE BINGO.

35:59.958 --> 36:02.728
- WHIP-O-RAMA!

36:02.761 --> 36:04.530
*

36:04.563 --> 36:07.599
- OH. G-51.

36:07.633 --> 36:10.802
[indistinct chatter]

36:10.836 --> 36:12.871
- ANY COLOR, ANY SIZE.

36:12.904 --> 36:14.806
[shouting, laughing]

36:14.840 --> 36:17.409
- A-34.

36:17.443 --> 36:18.944
- OOH, AHH!

36:18.977 --> 36:20.679
- AND AT CENTER STAGE,

36:20.712 --> 36:24.450
THE GRINDER!

36:24.483 --> 36:25.851
[crowd exclaims]

36:25.884 --> 36:28.854
- O-75.

36:33.725 --> 36:35.694
- OH, MY GOD.
- OH, WOW.

36:35.727 --> 36:37.496
- COME ON, EVERYONE,
STEP UP.

36:37.529 --> 36:40.466
COME ON.
IT'S BUTTHOLE BINGO.

36:42.634 --> 36:44.436
[pop]

36:44.470 --> 36:46.872
all: OH!

36:46.905 --> 36:49.475
- B-13.

36:49.508 --> 36:50.776
[indistinct chatter]

36:50.809 --> 36:53.512
- OVER 800 HAPPY,
SATISFIED CUSTOMERS,

36:53.545 --> 36:56.014
AND A LINE AROUND THE BLOCK
WAITING TO GET IN.

36:56.047 --> 36:57.449
- JESUS, BRIAN.

36:57.483 --> 36:58.850
- WHAT IS ALL THIS?

36:58.884 --> 37:00.852
[pop]

37:00.886 --> 37:03.322
- I-19.
- THIS IS BUTTHOLE BINGO.

37:03.355 --> 37:05.891
AND THAT IS ONE REMARKABLY
GIFTED YOUNG MAN.

37:05.924 --> 37:07.593
[pop]

37:07.626 --> 37:09.528
- THIS WASN'T
IN THE PROPOSAL YOU SUBMITTED.

37:09.561 --> 37:11.330
- YEAH, I TOOK
A FEW LIBERTIES.

37:11.363 --> 37:14.466
- WE'RE SUPPOSED TO REPRESENT
A POSITIVE GAY IMAGE.

37:14.500 --> 37:17.803
WHAT KIND OF MESSAGE DO YOU
THINK WE'RE SENDING HERE?

37:17.836 --> 37:19.605
- THAT ALL MEN
ARE CREATED HORNY,

37:19.638 --> 37:21.807
AND IT'S OKAY TO HAVE
A LITTLE DOWN-AND-DIRTY FUN.

37:21.840 --> 37:24.009
- YOU'VE REALLY GONE
TOO FAR.

37:24.042 --> 37:26.011
- YEAH, WELL IF IT'S
ANY CONSOLATION TO YOU,

37:26.044 --> 37:28.747
YOU'LL BE MAKING 10,000 OUT
OF HIS ASS ALONE.

37:28.780 --> 37:30.782
[all shout]

37:30.816 --> 37:33.752
- O-69.

37:33.785 --> 37:36.622
- "ME TO MAKE
ZE SUBSIDIARY SUBJECT.

37:36.655 --> 37:39.024
ZING, ETHAN, ZING!"

37:39.057 --> 37:40.892
[chuckles]

37:40.926 --> 37:42.394
- HEY.
- YEAH.

37:42.428 --> 37:43.829
- I'M GOING TO TAKE OFF.
- WHAT, ALREADY?

37:43.862 --> 37:45.063
- YEAH, I'M BEAT.

37:45.096 --> 37:46.565
- ALL RIGHT,
I'LL GO WITH YOU.

37:46.598 --> 37:48.767
- NO,
YOU CAN STAY HERE.

37:48.800 --> 37:50.569
I'LL SEE YOU AT HOME.

37:50.602 --> 37:53.038
- YOU SURE?
- MM-HMM.

37:53.071 --> 37:55.907
- OKAY.
LOVE YOU.

37:55.941 --> 37:59.511
- YOU TOO.

37:59.545 --> 38:05.517
[indistinct chatter]

38:05.551 --> 38:08.420
[alternative music]

38:08.454 --> 38:12.558
- * TONIGHT, TONIGHT

38:12.591 --> 38:14.025
* NO

38:28.440 --> 38:31.377
- CAN I COME IN?

38:47.626 --> 38:50.762
[clears throat]
YOU'RE JUST FINISHING DINNER?

38:50.796 --> 38:52.564
- JUST STARTING.

38:52.598 --> 38:56.368
3 OUNCES OF CHICKEN,
4 OUNCES OF LIMA BEANS.

38:56.402 --> 38:57.603
- IS THAT ENOUGH?

38:57.636 --> 38:59.004
YOU HAVE TO KEEP UP
YOUR STRENGTH.

38:59.037 --> 39:01.640
- RIGHT,
I HAVE TEN BLOW JOBS TO GIVE

39:01.673 --> 39:03.742
BEFORE I HIT THE HAY.

39:03.775 --> 39:05.744
- I WISH YOU WOULDN'T TALK
LIKE THAT.

39:05.777 --> 39:07.479
- IT'S HOW EXPERTS TALK.

39:07.513 --> 39:10.849
- YEAH, I KNOW.

39:10.882 --> 39:15.454
TWO OF THEM CAME
TO THE PRECINCT TODAY.

39:15.487 --> 39:17.623
THAT TALL SWISH-STICK?

39:17.656 --> 39:19.591
- EMMETT?

39:19.625 --> 39:21.159
- AND THE ONE WHO LOOKS
LIKE AN ACCOUNTANT.

39:21.192 --> 39:23.995
- TED.

39:24.029 --> 39:27.533
- THEY EXPLAINED
ALL ABOUT YOUR...EDUCATION,

39:27.566 --> 39:29.735
HOW YOU WENT TO THE HEAD
OF THE CLASS.

39:29.768 --> 39:31.169
- WELL, EMMETT'S GOT
A BIG MOUTH.

39:31.202 --> 39:35.407
IN MORE WAYS THAN ONE.

39:35.441 --> 39:37.075
WHAT ELSE
DID THEY TELL YOU?

39:37.108 --> 39:40.946
- THAT YOU DID IT
FOR ME.

39:40.979 --> 39:44.750
TO PLEASE ME.

39:44.783 --> 39:47.753
- I WOULDN'T DO THAT
FOR JUST ANYONE, YOU KNOW.

39:47.786 --> 39:50.622
- I KNOW.

39:50.656 --> 39:52.791
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT IT MEANS TO ME?

39:52.824 --> 39:55.561
THAT YOU WANTED TO GIVE ME
PLEASURE THAT MUCH?

39:55.594 --> 39:57.062
- I THOUGHT
THAT'S WHAT PEOPLE DO

